Property

Class Property

  • java.lang.Object
    • Property.Space
      • Property.Property
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Railroad, RealEstate, Utility

    public abstract class Property
extends Space
    The Property Class is an abstract class that inherits from Space This class keeps track of all properties for a property. An abstract method calculateRent is used for child classes to calculate the rent dependent on on the type of property.
